◆ sleep_duration_ns

uint64_t dlb_wait_profile_t::sleep_duration_ns

Duration, in nanoseconds, of the sleep. Valid only for profile type DLB_WAIT_TIMEOUT_SLEEP_POLL, ignored otherwise. Note that the OS may sleep the thread for longer than the requested duration.

◆ timeout_value_ns

uint64_t dlb_wait_profile_t::timeout_value_ns

Duration, in nanoseconds, to wait before timing out. Valid only for profile types DLB_WAIT_TIMEOUT_* and DLB_WAIT_INTR_LOW_POWER, ignored otherwise.
